    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "あむっ……ん～～～～！　このトルネードポテトという\nメニュー、とても美味しいですわ！",
      "startTime": 6.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "ポテトをらせん状にカットした面白い見た目で\n外はカリカリ、中はホクホク！",
      "startTime": 14,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "ソースやチーズ、トッピングも豊富で\nどう食べようか迷ってしまいますわね！",
      "startTime": 20.8000001271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか。それは良かったな、すず……",
      "startTime": 24.7666667938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "ええ！　……ってなんですの{user}さん\nそんな疲れた声、お祭りにふさわしくありませんわよ？",
      "startTime": 33.8333334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことは、俺が今両手に持っているものを\n見てからもう一度言ってくれ",
      "startTime": 41.8180006299,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、右手に焼肉串とチョコバナナ\n左手はたこ焼きにわたあめ……",
      "startTime": 48.1333334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "なぁんだ、満喫していたんですのね。でもそんなに\n沢山お買い物するだなんて。はしゃぎ過ぎではなくて？",
      "startTime": 56.3247894235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "全部すずが買った物だろう！？\n少し食べたらすぐ俺に渡して！",
      "startTime": 62.9953134537,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "最初に持つって言ったのは俺だけど……\nそれでも限度があると思うぞ！？",
      "startTime": 68.5666627248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうでしたわね……まぁそう怒らずに\nそのたこ焼き、食べて大丈夫ですわよ",
      "startTime": 75.7333293915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そういう問題じゃ……と、すず！\n前から人が来るぞ",
      "startTime": 82.3333324433,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1566.6666667000015,
          "startTime": 83.89999911
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "わぷっ、ごめんあそばせ……お怪我はありません？\nええ、私は無事ですわ。失礼いたしました……",
      "startTime": 90.4666657766,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "気が緩んでいましたわね、反省ですわ……\nそれにしても人が増えてきましたわね",
      "startTime": 100.2230707743,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4966.666666600006,
          "startTime": 100.2999986013
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐミニライブの時間だからな\nみんな会場へ向かっているんだろう",
      "startTime": 107.0999986013,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "そろそろ私達も移動をしましょうか……\nひゃっ、冷た……！",
      "startTime": 113.1333319347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "うわぁ、雨が！？　か、雷まで鳴ってるぞ！？\nすず、ひとまずあそこの休憩所で雨宿りしよう！",
      "startTime": 121.1666625977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rain-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 116.2757130306
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rain-03.m4a",
      "startTime": 116.2757130306
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "待ってくださいまし！　今、私達が\n向かうべきは運営本部ですわ！",
      "startTime": 127.5999975841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "ミニライブがどうなってしまうのか\n直接聞きに行きましょう！",
      "startTime": 133.599995931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "うう……どんどん雨脚が強くなっていますわね\nこのままだと……",
      "startTime": 143.6333309174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ひとまずミニライブの開始は見合わせ、雨が止まないと\n中止も視野に入れてるってことだったからな",
      "startTime": 150.2333212535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "ミニライブといえども、参加する方々にとっては\n大切な晴れ舞台だというのに……はぁ……",
      "startTime": 157.599995931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そう、だな……だがこればかりはどうしようもない……\nあまり落ちこみ過ぎないでくれ……",
      "startTime": 168.4666642507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、心配してくださるんですのね……\nですが、ただ落ち込んでいた訳ではありませんの",
      "startTime": 175.1529150159,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "また昔を思い出していたんですの\n麻奈様が出た星見まつりもこんな大雨でしたわね……",
      "startTime": 183.199995931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "今でも鮮明に覚えていますのよ\n麻奈様が歌い出したら奇跡が起きたんですもの",
      "startTime": 191.8333292644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02-suz018.m4a",
      "text": "まるで麻奈様の歌声に応えるように\n雨雲が散り散りになり、星が降ってきて……",
      "startTime": 199.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_02-suz019.m4a",
      "text": "あんな素敵な経験、絶対に忘れられませんわ\nおかげであの日から、私は麻奈様に夢中なんですのよ",
